    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一个小型定居点开始，你将收集资源，建造建筑，并逐步扩大你的影响力。随着你的势力不断壮大，你将面临内部和外部的挑战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设你的定居点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/c63c690db8b29726a8b52b2cccf2e55f.poster.avif?t=1772484495\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/c63c690db8b29726a8b52b2cccf2e55f.webm?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/c63c690db8b29726a8b52b2cccf2e55f.mp4?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源并建造建筑来发展你的阵营。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >指挥强大的军队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/fca7ba2bc9d2fc3c9644e7f25a24ff27.poster.avif?t=1772484495\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/fca7ba2bc9d2fc3c9644e7f25a24ff27.webm?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/fca7ba2bc9d2fc3c9644e7f25a24ff27.mp4?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建你的军队并招募独特的英雄和佣兵来领导它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索地下城</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/343750cde27e56eccdc5647f3992373a.poster.avif?t=1772484495\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/343750cde27e56eccdc5647f3992373a.webm?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/343750cde27e56eccdc5647f3992373a.mp4?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突袭程序生成的地下城以获取盔甲和强大的武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发展你的阵营</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/2e55bddeba5ca22f0401f092b204e486.poster.avif?t=1772484495\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/2e55bddeba5ca22f0401f092b204e486.webm?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/2e55bddeba5ca22f0401f092b204e486.mp4?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >研究新技术并解锁新能力，以保持领先于其他阵营。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >参与外交</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/1e16fa0e45f4f13a1bfd2fc95840a955.poster.avif?t=1772484495\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/1e16fa0e45f4f13a1bfd2fc95840a955.webm?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238690/extras/1e16fa0e45f4f13a1bfd2fc95840a955.mp4?t=1772484495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结成同盟、开展贸易或对其他阵营宣战。</p>",
